==交通==

[[跨苏拉威西公路|跨苏拉威西公路]]经过帕卢，沿此公路可前往[[望加锡|望加锡]]、[[万鸦老|万鸦老]]、[[哥伦打洛|哥伦打洛]]等城市，此公路向北部分路段正在升级建设以及维护修缮中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/81533/manado-people-ask-govt-accelerate-trans-sulawesi |title=Manado people ask govt accelerate Trans Sulawesi |last= |first= |date=2012-04-22 |website=www.antaranews.com |publisher= |access-date=2017-07-15 |quote=Some roads in Minahasa Selatan, Bolaang North Bongondow and Nort Gorontalo are now under construction |archive-date=2016-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129192226/http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/81533/manado-people-ask-govt-accelerate-trans-sulawesi |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

跨苏拉威西铁路起点在[[望加锡|望加锡]]，未来规划铁路线还将经过[[马穆朱|马穆朱]]、帕卢、[[哥伦打洛|哥伦打洛]]、[[比通|比通]]等城市最终延伸到[[万鸦老|万鸦老]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shangbaoindonesia.com/indonesia-berita/%E4%BD%90%E7%A7%91%E5%A8%81%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%8D%97%E8%8B%8F%E7%9C%81%E8%A7%86%E5%AF%9F%E8%B7%A8%E8%8B%8F%E6%8B%89%E5%A8%81%E8%A5%BF%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%9B.html |title=佐科威总统访问南苏省 视察跨苏拉威西铁路工程进度 |publisher=印度尼西亚商报 |date=2015年11月25日 |accessdate=2017年7月1日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805100936/http://www.shangbaoindonesia.com/indonesia-berita/%E4%BD%90%E7%A7%91%E5%A8%81%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%8D%97%E8%8B%8F%E7%9C%81%E8%A7%86%E5%AF%9F%E8%B7%A8%E8%8B%8F%E6%8B%89%E5%A8%81%E8%A5%BF%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%9B.html |archive-date=2017-08-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

帕卢港主要码头位于帕卢湾东岸，城区东北方向<ref>{{cite map |publisher=Kementerian Pekerjaan Umum |title=Peta Infrastruktur Kota Palu |trans_title=帕卢市基础设施地图 |map= |mapurl= |date= |year=2013 |url=http://loketpeta.pu.go.id/peta-infrastruktur-kota-palu-2013 |scale=1:20,000 |series= |version= |cartography= |page= |pages= |section= |inset= |edition= |location= |language=id |format= |isbn= |id= |ref= |accessdate= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428193035/http://loketpeta.pu.go.id/peta-infrastruktur-kota-palu-2013 |archivedate=2017-04-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

[[穆提亚拉西斯朱弗里机场|穆提亚拉西斯朱弗里机场]]位于城市东南部的南帕卢区境内，有飞往[[雅加达|雅加达]]、[[望加锡|望加锡]]和[[泗水_(印尼)|泗水]]等印尼大城市和中苏省各小城镇的航班。

==经济特区==

帕卢经济特区总面积1500公顷<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kemlu.go.id/guangzhou/lc/berita-agenda/berita-perwakilan/Pages/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%89%B9%E5%8C%BA.aspx |title=印尼经济特区 |last= |first= |date=2015-07-15 |website=www.kemlu.go.id |publisher=印度尼西亚驻广州总领事馆 |access-date=2017-09-22 |quote= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923052739/http://www.kemlu.go.id/guangzhou/lc/berita-agenda/berita-perwakilan/Pages/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%89%B9%E5%8C%BA.aspx |archive-date=2017-09-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，是苏拉威西经济走廊的组成部分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://economists-pick-research.hktdc.com/business-news/article/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E7%AE%80%E8%AE%AF/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E8%97%89%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%89%B9%E5%8C%BA%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA/imn/sc/1/1X000000/1X0AAL45.htm |title=印尼有意藉经济特区计划发展旅游基建 |last= |first= |date=2017-07-06 |website=economists-pick-research.hktdc.com |publisher=经贸研究 |access-date=2017-09-23 |quote= |archive-date=2017-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170920142518/http://economists-pick-research.hktdc.com/business-news/article/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E7%AE%80%E8%AE%AF/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E8%97%89%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%89%B9%E5%8C%BA%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA/imn/sc/1/1X000000/1X0AAL45.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。帕卢地区拥有兴建冶炼厂以及发展农业、矿业的潜力，将建设冶炼业、物流业、橡胶产业、电子工业以及[[沃尔沃|沃尔沃]]装配厂等工厂，其中，中国企业在帕卢经济特区物流业、电子工业、冶炼业和汽车工业（沃尔沃）等领域有投资<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shangbaoindonesia.com/indonesia-berita/%E8%8B%8F%E6%8B%89%E5%A8%81%E8%A5%BF%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E9%80%9A%E5%92%8C%E5%B7%B4%E9%B2%81-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8B%9F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%89%B9%E5%8C%BA.html |title=苏拉威西的比通和巴鲁 政府拟定为经济特区 |last= |first= |date=2013-07-26 |website=www.shangbaoindonesia.com |publisher=印度尼西亚商报 |access-date=2017-09-23 |quote= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923050910/http://www.shangbaoindonesia.com/indonesia-berita/%E8%8B%8F%E6%8B%89%E5%A8%81%E8%A5%BF%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E9%80%9A%E5%92%8C%E5%B7%B4%E9%B2%81-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8B%9F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%89%B9%E5%8C%BA.html |archive-date=2017-09-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chinachamber.co/Detail.aspx?id=280 |title=中国投资家要在巴鲁建钢铁厂 |last= |first= |date=2017-09-23 |website=印度尼西亚中国商会总会 |publisher=国际日报 |access-date=2017-09-23 |quote= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923095649/http://www.chinachamber.co/Detail.aspx?id=280 |archive-date=2017-09-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。帕卢经济特区的发展重点集中在矿产加工业、农用工业、制造业以及物流业<ref>{{cite web |url=http://intl.ce.cn/specials/zxgjzh/201408/14/t20140814_3354478.shtml |title=印尼将在东部地区新建5个经济特区 |last= |first= |date=2014-08-14 |website=intl.ce.cn |publisher=中国经济网 |access-date=2017-09-22 |quote= |archive-date=2017-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921001555/http://intl.ce.cn/specials/zxgjzh/201408/14/t20140814_3354478.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==印度尼西亚滑翔伞公开锦标赛==

[[File:COLLECTIE_TROPENMUSEUM_Berglandschap_met_rijstvelden_en_paalwoningen_in_de_omgeving_van_Palu_TMnr_20018497.jpg|thumb]]

印度尼西亚[[滑翔伞|滑翔伞]]公开锦标赛是[[世界锦标赛|世锦赛]]系列中第一个在印度尼西亚地区举行的公开赛，于2011年6月19日至25日在距离帕卢{{convert|30|km|abbr=off}}的瓦尤村（Wayu）海拔800米的马坦蒂马利山（Matantimali）举行，来自[[日本|日本]]、[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]、[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[韩国|韩国]]和[[瑞士|瑞士]]等国的78名滑翔伞运动员参加了本赛事<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/72882/indonesia-hosts-paragliding-open-championship-in-palu |newspaper=Antara News |title=Indonesia hosts paragliding open championship in Palu |last=Maruli |first=Aditia |date=2011-06-18 |accessdate= |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040256/http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/72882/indonesia-hosts-paragliding-open-championship-in-palu |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

